# Release Strategy

Follow package-first release behavior:

1. Validate packaged-artifact behavior.
2. Publish through standard automation.
3. Verify downstream consumer install/update path.
4. Feed release friction back into task-engine tasks (and keep the task store plus maintainer phase narrative aligned — **`docs/maintainers/ROADMAP.md`** on disk for humans; agents use **`wk`** + **`.ai/RELEASING.md`** per **`agent-doc-routing.mdc`**).

